          <p>FilterFive is a business-to-business platform that helps local businesses request customer reviews via SMS. When you receive an SMS from a FilterFive-powered business, it means:</p>
          <ol>
            <li>You recently visited or did business with a local business</li>
            <li>That business uses FilterFive to request customer feedback</li>
            <li>You provided your phone number and consent to receive a review request</li>
