          <p>You can stop receiving messages at any time by replying with any of these keywords:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>STOP</strong></li>
            <li><strong>UNSUBSCRIBE</strong></li>
            <li><strong>CANCEL</strong></li>
            <li><strong>END</strong></li>
            <li><strong>QUIT</strong></li>
          </ul>
          <p>Opt-out requests are processed <strong>immediately and automatically</strong>. Once you opt out, you will not receive any further messages.</p>
        </section>

